le": "Ma'am, you're nowhere near as tired as we are. ", "last_comment_created": 1779868134837, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 163, "score_up": 863, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 180, "created": 1779765121000, "id": "2059110278512427252", "video": {"preview": "https://pbs.twimg.com/amplify_video_thumb/2059109990019760128/img/006-jC0DqzgcNt-q.jpg", "mpeg": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2059109990019760128/pl/tHS2iHUtONYg0QEF.m3u8?v=544", "aspectRatio": [9, 16], "heightRatio": 177, "type": "video/mp4", "url": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2059109990019760128/vid/avc1/320x568/c8X2T8tZAftdhQVy.mp4"}, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2048200134840999937/kV3ac-Al_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Viral Videos\u2122\ufe0f", "username": "ViralVideos"}, "content": "Yet another black female who ensures she has her hair and nails done and who also thinks the government is her baby daddy.\n\nHow about you stop getting pregnant and instead go get a job to support yourself and all of your kids?", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 834}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsdopVN3", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 68, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8642109, "raw_content": "Of course I did.\n\nI was divorced and had the kids for the weekend.  She wanted me to call mom to pick her up.  \n\nInstead, I drew her a map, gave her a flashlight and watched her walk out the front door.\n\nI secretly followed her.  Two houses away I found her crying.  I picked her up and carried her back to my house.  She fell asleep watching a Disney movie in my arms.\n\nThe next morning, she was soundly sleeping with my house mate's dog in a cardboard refrigerator box.\n\nShe still calls me \"Daddy\".  \n\nI am truly blessed.", "author": "KuzoKevin", "created": 1779851104029, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "KuzoKevin", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "So my 28 year old daughter asked me tonight if I actually encouraged her walk home, a couple miles...at night...when she was five.", "last_comment_created": 1779865365195, "content": "<p>Of course I did.</p>\n<p>I was divorced and had the kids for the weekend.  She wanted me to call mom to pick her up.</p>\n<p>Instead, I drew her a map, gave her a flashlight and watched her walk out the front door.</p>\n<p>I secretly followed her.  Two houses away I found her crying.  I picked her up and carried her back to my house.  She fell asleep watching a Disney movie in my arms.</p>\n<p>The next morning, she was soundly sleeping with my house mate's dog in a cardboard refrigerator box.</p>\n<p>She still calls me &quot;Daddy&quot;.</p>\n<p>I am truly blessed.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 9, "score_up": 68, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsdopVha", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 62, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8642152, "raw_content": "", "author": "greatpumpkin", "created": 